paragraphs.title: Overview of Root Causes per Top components (last one month)
paragraphs.text:
%jdbc(hive)
select  c.week, 
p.name, sum(c.status) as open_cases,
sum(
case
    when rc.name like "%Product Defect%" Then 1
    else 0
end) as Bug, 
sum(
case
    when rc.name like "%Environment%" Then 1
    else 0
end) as env,
sum(
case
    when rc.name like "%Education - Configuration%" Then 1
    else 0
end) as config,
sum(
case
    when rc.name like "%Non Configuration%" Then 1
    else 0
end) as non_config,
sum(
case
    when rc.name like "%Data Issue%" Then 1
    else 0
end) as data_inconsistency
from cases c
join product p
on c.componentID = p.ID
join RootCause rc
on c.RootCauseID = rc.ID
where p.name in ("Ambari", "Hive", "HDFS", "Hbase"

    from cases
    order by year_week desc
    limit 5
)

-- monthly top account

select year, month, name, rank, count 
from(
    select year, month(c.dateopen) as month, a.name as name, 
    Dense_Rank() over (partition by c.year, month(c.dateopen) order by count(c.casenum) desc) as rank, 
    count(c.casenum) as count
    from cases c
    join account a
    on c.accountId = a.id 
    where concat(year,"-", week) > add_months(current_date, -2)
    group by c.year, month(c.dateopen), a.name 
    having count >= 2
    order by year, month, rank) t
where t.rank <=5

%jdbc(hive)
select c.year, 
--c.week, 
month(c.dateopen) as month,
p.name, sum(c.status) as open_case,
sum(
case
    when rc.name like "%Product Defect%" Then 1
    else 0
end) as Bug, 
sum(
case
    when rc.name like "%Environment%" Then 1
    else 0
end) as env,
sum(
case
    when rc.name like "%Education - Configuration%" Then 1
    else 0
end) as config,
sum(
case
    when rc.name like "%Non Configuration%" Then 1
    else 0
end) as non_config,
sum(
case
    when rc.name like "%Data Issue%" Then 1
    else 0
end) as data_inconsistency
from cases c
join product p
on c.componentID = p.ID
join RootCause rc
on c.RootCauseID = rc.ID
where p.name in ("Ambari", "Hive", "HDFS", "Hbase"
--, "Nifi", "Oozie", "Yarn", "Ranger"
)
and rc.name in ("Customer Environment (Non HDP)", "Education - Configuration", "Education - Non Configuration", "Product Defect", "Data Issue")
group by c.year,

month(c.dateopen),
